{"title":"Macworld Podcast: What to expect from Apple in 2025","link":"https://www.macworld.com/article/2340579/macworld-podcast-what-to-expect-from-apple-in-2025.html","date":1716451200000,"content":"<p><a href=\"https://www.macworld.com\">Macworld</a></p>\n\n<div>\n<section><div></div></section>\n\n\n\n<p>Technology is all about what’s coming next, and in this episode of the Macworld Podcast, we’re talking about what we can see from Apple in 2025</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Technology is all about what’s coming next, and in this episode of the Macworld Podcast, we’re talking about what we can see from Apple in 2025! A super thin iPhone, a new Mac Studio, updated AirTags and more! Find out more on the show!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This is episode 885 with <a href=\"https://www.macworld.com/author/Jason-Cross/\" target=\"_blank\">Jason Cross</a>, <a href=\"https://www.macworld.com/author/Michael-Simon/\" target=\"_blank\">Michael Simon</a>, and <a href=\"https://www.macworld.com/author/Roman-Loyola/\" target=\"_blank\">Roman Loyola</a>.</p>\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://go.redirectingat.com/?id=111346X1569486&amp;url=https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/what-to-expect-from-apple-in-2025/id563933198&amp;xcust=1-1-2340579-7-0-0&amp;sref=https://www.macworld.com/feed\" target=\"_blank\">Click here to go to the Macworld Podcast Episode 885 on Apple Podcasts</a></p>\n\n\n<h2>Listen to episode 885 on Spotify</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><div>\n\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>Get info </h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Click on the links below for more information on what was discussed on the show. </p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.macworld.com/article/2337606/the-2025-iphone-could-feature-a-thin-redesigned-ultra-high-end-model.html\" target=\"_blank\">Next year’s iPhone could feature a thin, redesigned ultra high-end model</a> </li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://www.macworld.com/article/2338490/mac-studio-pro-refresh-2025.html\" target=\"_blank\">Don’t expect the Mac Studio and Mac Pro to be updated at WWDC–or in 2024</